This repository contains methods for detection and correction of batch effected data. It can be applied to any omics data in the format - features x counts.

The scripts in this repository under 'workflow' are adjusted for flow cytometry data.

The methods used are documented under the folders 'Batch effect detection' and 'Batch effect correction'


.
├── Batch effect correction 
│   ├── BatchAdjust.R
│   ├── CytoNorm.R
│   └── CytofBatchAdjust.R
├── Batch effect detection
│   └── Beclear_batch_effect_detection.R
├── Data
│   ├── ChannelsToAdjust.txt
│   ├── batch_data.xlsx
│   └── panel.xlsx
├── README
├── Results
│   ├── All plots.pptx
